111 void callbackOdometry(const nav_msgs::Odometry::ConstPtr& odometry)
112 {
113  poseOdom[0] = odometry -> pose.pose.position.x;
114  poseOdom[1] = odometry -> pose.pose.position.y;
115 
116  Quaternion orientationQ;
117  orientationQ.x = odometry -> pose.pose.orientation.x;
118  orientationQ.y = odometry -> pose.pose.orientation.y;
119  orientationQ.z = odometry -> pose.pose.orientation.z;
120  orientationQ.w = odometry -> pose.pose.orientation.w;
121 
122  EulerAngles orientationE;
123  orientationE = ToEulerAngles(orientationQ);
124  poseOdom[2] = (orientationE.yaw*180.0)/PI;
125 
126  initialOdom = true;
127 }

245  std::chrono::duration<double> durationReal = finish - start;

247  break;
